Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海上的波濤聲 比平時更加清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炫目的月光充滿了天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那月光如此溫暖地 擁抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 若能盡情享受世界給我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 新威尼斯的秋天快要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡很快就要迎來寒冬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為愛麗絲先行成為正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的共同練習已經變成了與藍華兩個人的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華啊 開始變冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋天就要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有兩個人的共同練習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是讓人想起我們剛剛相識的情形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然現在說完全不寂寞是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是非常值得高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們也不能輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一起為了成為正式領航員努力吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不能再跟妳一起共同練習了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是一直努力著 夢想著這一天的到來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳晉級為正式領航員 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…我就知道燈里會這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有一件事想跟妳說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:33.59,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那片 蔚藍的大海與風…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 藍華她晉級為正式領航員了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是個好消息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稱號是Rozen Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是薔薇女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定下來是那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃一直都在煩惱這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候進行藍華的晉級考試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為藍華不僅僅是要成為正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還要背負整個姬屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過如果是藍華的話一定不會有問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實呢 我還有一個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑塔·露琪亞附近要開一家姬屋的分店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(265,440)\fs20}Santa Lucia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華要到那裡擔任分店長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她說以後會變得很忙很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是件值得高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華卻哭得很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:05:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天將對妳進行正式領航員晉級考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在好緊張哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡不著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我終於要面對晉級考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為實在緊張得睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以雖然是晚上 我還是出去練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 終於等到這一天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像也開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長 謝謝你陪我出來練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來 就跟平時練習一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了 不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛從中學的同學會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就弄丟錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明牢牢繫在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 鬢子妳這麼晚在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天…是我的正式領航員晉級考試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爺最近也要進行晉級考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常瞭解鬢子妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 曉 我找到你的錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？在哪找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉在店裡的洗手間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…居然在那種怎麼都不可能掉的地方掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭錢包 你給我去廁所睡覺吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點 曉 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？燈里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這麼晚還在練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子啊 考試加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望天氣不要變壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得努力睡一覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 遠方的天空很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午應該就放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晉級考試…不如延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是個重要的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新選一個天氣好的日子再考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直等著這一天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是艾莉西亞前輩決定給我考試的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天對於我來說 已經很重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要是下午也一直下的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備工作都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱水袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 真體貼的服務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座位和毯子都暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡到大運河之間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從任何一個地方都能遙望大鐘樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 雨過天晴之後我最推薦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這條小路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是賽艇的選手先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的船槳都是自己做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的路要由自己來闖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不這樣的話 就會留下遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年我要奪冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終於到了大運河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(515,440)\fs20}Canal Grande
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新威尼斯的版圖上畫出一個倒S型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大運河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人您冷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是橫跨大運河的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里亞托橋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ponte di Rialto
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也是水上通行之人與橋上眺望之人邂逅的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉 她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 伍迪 我們按計劃行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hurray～ hurray～ 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}hurray～ hurray～ 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}加油啊 燈里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是曉先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞小姐也要加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快給我下來 小心掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕陽西下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖馬可廣場和被稱為Lagoon的瀉湖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不斷變換著色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像被溫暖的顏色所環抱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在其中不斷被治癒一樣不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 操縱鳳尾舟的技巧和導遊詞都很熟練了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還能感覺到燈里獨特的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…非常重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 這條水路…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 平時是禁止新人進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 現在我們可以進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝著水路盡頭的 燈里的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很狹窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比以前任何一條水路都要窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到還有這樣的水路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人不可思議地 感覺不到慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感覺到 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三人總是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從船槳傳達到指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深邃而靜謐的 水的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與大家度過的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支撐著現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有力地推動著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 這次的鳳尾舟之旅太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠靜而恬然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像鳳尾舟與海水融合在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這是最後的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡開始的路線由燈里妳來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成為怎樣的正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要由燈里自己來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成為怎樣的正式領航員嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事物即將有所轉變之時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都踏上了屬於自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像相互催發著對方的變化一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連鎖重疊起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切 從最初都已經被命運所決定一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要成為的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是像祖母那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像艾莉西亞前輩這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像亞利亞公司一樣的領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從妳來到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的世界就翻開了新的一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都開始閃爍著迷人的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人施展了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像溫柔地環抱著AQUA的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延伸到無盡遠方的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空與大海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能與妳相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的海藍寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(457,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海藍…寶石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深邃的…藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳晉級成為正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 我是正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直一直…都憧憬著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從踏足這顆星球那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件重要的事情要跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.25,0:24:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷變換的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.78,0:24:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恬靜溫馨的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一個人的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 我將啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 嶄新的開端…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
